docs.abstract: If you’re willing to search, you can get a vacation deal. You’ll even be able to check a bag at no extra cost.
docs.snippet: If you’re willing to search, you can get a vacation deal. You’ll even be able to check a bag at no extra cost.
docs.lead_paragraph: Over the past decade, airlines have developed a reputation for nickel-and-diming their passengers. For the most part, the days of free checked baggage and free seat assignments are long gone. Even the days of free carry-on bags seem to be dwindling. And tickets are still expensive enough to be a major purchase for most fliers, especially around the holidays.

headline.main: Good Cheap Flights Still Exist. Here’s How to Find Them.
